            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Start by hanging from a pull-up bar with your palms facing away from you.",
                    "Engage your shoulder blades and pull them down towards your hips.",
                    "Slowly lift your legs up towards the bar, keeping them straight and together.",
                    "Continue to lift your legs until your body is parallel to the ground.",
                    "Hold this position for as long as you can, aiming for at least 10 seconds.",
                    "To release, slowly lower your legs back down to the starting position."
